rComments: The class was a 2nd half course. 25% Midterm, 25% Final, 25% Response Papers, and 25% Group Project. If you go to class and do well on the group project, you'll get a good grade. I only studied for a few hours for the midterm and final and got As. Both exams were scantron. On the downside, this is a very boring class. Meet twice a week for 3 hrs.
